HR 360 Original 2026 Regular Session Edmonston
Creates the Task Force on Child Well-Being, Parental Bonds, and Family Court Fairness to
study the administration of justice in family courts, the adequacy of evidentiary standards
used in custody and visitation determinations, and the impact of rising costs of custody
litigation and related proceedings on families.
Requires the task force to submit a report of its findings and recommendations for legislation
to the La. House of Representatives by Feb. 15, 2027.
